commit 1da17d7cf8e2c4b60163d54300f72c02f510327c
Author: Andrey Smirnov <andrew.smirnov@gmail.com>
Date:   Mon Jul 29 12:52:15 2019 -0700

    tty: serial: fsl_lpuart: Use appropriate lpuart32_* I/O funcs
    
